{"tid":1680921,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊偉雄：20支損毀監控燈柱回復照明　將配合5G監控發展","createTime":"2019-10-29T06:03:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T10:26:39.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f95de58c328e3235baa7cdfbccea514b5f52ef3f","tid":1680921,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:03:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488797-20191029.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488797-20191029.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFP1pzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=c4650e42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488797-20191029.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f12ffcc0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488797-20191029.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1488797_1_L_20191029131416.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1488797_1_L_20191029131416.jpg&h=b1f3121f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在立法會資訊科技及廣播事務委員會會議，創新及科技局局長楊偉雄解釋有關新一份施政報告的創科政策。<br />\n<br />\n經民聯議員盧偉國關注最近有智慧燈柱被破壞，反映有市民不明白政府推行大數據的政策。創新及科技局局長楊偉雄表示，發展智能燈柱的所有程序會在陽光下進行，所有安裝過程也經過區議會認可，局方最近已引入第三方專家意見審視，未來會更加公開貼地諮詢公眾。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，留意到有20支智慧燈柱損毀，現已回復照明功能，未來會繼續配合5G發展，例如收集環保方面的數據。"},{"pid":"3f0d5d5953ebc7c6370847d8ba0d5c7ba6b3783b","tid":1680921,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:04:13.000Z","msg":"教大家一招KO林鄭成個取消區議會計劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680857\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680857</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7af39a15424989a6e9056edd0c7851051daac0a9","tid":1680921,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:04:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jc8536k.jpg\" data-th